    • fillForm

      public void fillForm(int selectedIndex, int partId, String partName, double partPrice, int partStock, int partMin, int partMax, String type, String partSwitch)
      Places the parameter values from the selected part into the text fields of the Modify Part screen.
      Parameters:
      selectedIndex - index of the selected part
      partId - ID of the selected part
      partName - name of the selected part
      partPrice - price of the selected part
      partStock - inventory level of the selected part
      partMin - minimum inventory level of the selected part
      partMax - maximum inventory level of the selected part
      type - indicator of whether the selected part is In-house or Outsourced
      partSwitch - seventh parameter of the selected part, either Machine ID or Company Name
